(firstQuint)Extended Release Naltrexone for Opioid-Dependent Youth.

 This proposed study is a 6-month, two-group randomized clinical trial of XR-NTX v.

 TAU for 340 opioid-dependent youth ages 15-21.

 The study will be conducted at Mountain Manor Treatment Center, a community drug treatment program in Baltimore.

 TAU will consist of buprenorphine treatment of opioid withdrawal followed by counseling with or without continued buprenorphine.

